Reaver’s Touch	SOURCEPAGE:p.42	SCHOOL:Necromancy	CASTTIME:1 action	RANGE:Touch	COMPS:V, S	DURATION:Instantaneous	DESC: The touch of your hand drains a target’s life energy, allowing you to sacrifice animals and other creatures to make their vitality your own. Make a melee spell attack against the target. You have advantage on the attack if your target is a beast. On a hit, the target takes 1d6 necrotic damage, and you gain temporary hit points equal to half the damage inflicted (rounded up). The spell’s damage increases by 1d6 when you reach 5th level (2d6), 11th level (3d6), and 17th level (4d6).
